    <title>myfristtime</title>
    <link href="/2025/03/23/myfristtime/"/>
    <url>/2025/03/23/myfristtime/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p align="center">  <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alexnaiman/alexnaiman/master/resources/welcomeglitch.gif" width="50px" /></p><h2 id="👋-Hello"><a href="#👋-Hello" class="headerlink" title="👋 Hello!"></a>👋 Hello!</h2><p align="center">  <samp>    My name is <em>AAAA_ALAN</em>. I am a sophomore ACM competitor, studying algorithms and machine learning (AI).      Enthusiast in exploring new and interesting areas of computer science.      I enjoy working with JavaScript, React, and React Native.      Always curious, eager to learn, and keen to help the community.  </samp></p><p align="center">  <img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/VgCDAzcKvsR6OM0uWg/giphy.gif" width="50" alt="learning gif" />  <b><i>Learning while HOPING & HUSTLING!!!</i></b>  <img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/7j2hfyeVcDtf2/giphy.gif" width="50" alt="hustle gif" /></p><hr><h2 id="🧠-About-Me"><a href="#🧠-About-Me" class="headerlink" title="🧠 About Me"></a>🧠 About Me</h2><ul><li>💬 Pronouns: <strong>He&#x2F;Him</strong></li><li>📚 Currently focused on algorithm studies and competitive programming</li><li>🐍 Learning Python and C++</li><li>🤝 Looking to collaborate in open-source projects <code>(newbie)</code></li><li>🛡️ Seeking insights into cybersecurity!</li><li>😄 Fun Fact: I’m always ready to help if it’s within my skills!</li></ul><p align="right">  <img src="https://media.tenor.com/images/df8c44a1d20ab367fdcb21880985fd33/tenor.gif" width="200" /></p><hr><h2 id="📈-GitHub-Stats"><a href="#📈-GitHub-Stats" class="headerlink" title="📈 GitHub Stats"></a>📈 GitHub Stats</h2><p align="center">  <img src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api?username=pa-her0&count_private=true&show_icons=true&theme=great-gatsby" alt="GitHub Stats" />  <img src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/top-langs/?username=pa-her0&layout=compact&theme=great-gatsby" alt="Top Languages" /></p><hr><h2 id="🧮-Profile-Visitor-Count"><a href="#🧮-Profile-Visitor-Count" class="headerlink" title="🧮 Profile Visitor Count"></a>🧮 Profile Visitor Count</h2><p align="center">  <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/saadeghi/saadeghi/master/dino.gif" width="1000" />  <br/>  <img src="https://profile-counter.glitch.me/ALan_jie/count.svg" /></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
